snippet.description: Today, in our village, we cook a spicy chicken recipe using Chili, Garlic, and sauces. First, we fry marinated chicken and mix it with some veggies and sauces in an open vessel. This chicken recipe is best for starters, and it will be delicious with a slight spiciness.

snippet.title: Tauba Tauba | Bad Newz | Vicky Kaushal | Triptii Dimri | Karan Aujla | In cinemas 19th July
snippet.description:
Experience the magic of Karan Aujla, Triptii Dimri and Vicky Kaushal's first-ever collaboration in "Tauba Tauba" from Bad Newz! This high-energy dance number is guaranteed to make you move. Get ready to dance like never before!

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Composer - Karan Aujla
Singer - Karan Aujla
Lyricist - Karan Aujla
Music Producer - Yeah Proof
Special Thanks Azeem Dayani
Mixing And Mastering - Hanish Taneja
Choreographer - Bosco- Ceaser
Song Editor- Adele Jerome Pereira
Production Designer- Manini Mishra
DOP- Santhana Krishnan Ravichandran
Costume Designer- Samidha Wangnoo

Bad Newz in cinemas 19th July.

Amazon Prime presents
In association with Dharma Productions and Leo Media Collective
A Leo Media Collective production
BAD NEWZ
Starring Vicky Kaushal, Triptii Dimri and Ammy Virk
Directed by Anand Tiwari
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Amritpal Singh Bindra & Anand Tiwari
Written by Ishita Moitra & Tarun Dudeja

Lyrics:

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4
Oh le liya ladki ne dil humara,
Abhi thoda saaf nahi lag raha irada,
Choti bahaut lambi nahi rakhi hai mutiyar ne,
Haaye dikhta nahi hai parranda, dikhta hai Prada,
Figure se lagti Latino
Ek baar batado itni kyun ho shaukinon,
Kal hi tum Italy se aayi hai marjaaniye, aur purse tenu Paris se mangvaya hai Valentino
Haan tujhe kyun na dekhu, tujhse kya seekhu, tujh mein kya likhu?

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Hum hai malana aur who kief,
Aira-gaira dekhti nahi waise toh shareef hoon, yahaan par kehti hai too much desi hai,
isliye chill kare London aur party at Ibiza hai, humaare liye bilkul bhee free nahi lagti, IG
story pe toh Bora Bora , awaaz tumhari sohniye surilee noori ke (Old Punjabi singer) jaise
lagti, jab kamar hile “Nora” lagti,
Milna dass de (bata de), tha (jagah) dass de, meri jaan dass de (bata de),

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Haaye! Mitron se aankh tumhari maange kangna (mujhse tumhari aankh Kangana maang
rahi hai),
Abhi main banwa dunga mujhe bata toh sahi,
Jaan maang lo main tujhpe jaan waar (jaan nyochavar karna) du, khud nikal jaayegi tu
hass toh sahi, tujhmein nasha pehli tod (daaru) jaisa hai kude (girl), sohniye daru ka toh
naam lagta hai, hum se zyaada tumhari popularity ho gayi hai, tum bahar nikli toh sadko
par jam (traffic jam) lagta hai,
Haa... baat maan meri, mehman meri, tum ho jaan meri,

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Experience the magic of Karan Aujla, Triptii Dimri and Vicky Kaushal's first-ever collaboration in "Tauba Tauba" from Bad Newz! This high-energy dance number is guaranteed to make you move. Get ready to dance like never before!

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Composer - Karan Aujla
Singer - Karan Aujla
Lyricist - Karan Aujla
Music Producer - Yeah Proof
Special Thanks Azeem Dayani
Mixing And Mastering - Hanish Taneja
Choreographer - Bosco- Ceaser
Song Editor- Adele Jerome Pereira
Production Designer- Manini Mishra
DOP- Santhana Krishnan Ravichandran
Costume Designer- Samidha Wangnoo

Bad Newz in cinemas 19th July.

Amazon Prime presents
In association with Dharma Productions and Leo Media Collective
A Leo Media Collective production
BAD NEWZ
Starring Vicky Kaushal, Triptii Dimri and Ammy Virk
Directed by Anand Tiwari
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Amritpal Singh Bindra & Anand Tiwari
Written by Ishita Moitra & Tarun Dudeja

Lyrics:

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4
Oh le liya ladki ne dil humara,
Abhi thoda saaf nahi lag raha irada,
Choti bahaut lambi nahi rakhi hai mutiyar ne,
Haaye dikhta nahi hai parranda, dikhta hai Prada,
Figure se lagti Latino
Ek baar batado itni kyun ho shaukinon,
Kal hi tum Italy se aayi hai marjaaniye, aur purse tenu Paris se mangvaya hai Valentino
Haan tujhe kyun na dekhu, tujhse kya seekhu, tujh mein kya likhu?

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Hum hai malana aur who kief,
Aira-gaira dekhti nahi waise toh shareef hoon, yahaan par kehti hai too much desi hai,
isliye chill kare London aur party at Ibiza hai, humaare liye bilkul bhee free nahi lagti, IG
story pe toh Bora Bora , awaaz tumhari sohniye surilee noori ke (Old Punjabi singer) jaise
lagti, jab kamar hile “Nora” lagti,
Milna dass de (bata de), tha (jagah) dass de, meri jaan dass de (bata de),

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Haaye! Mitron se aankh tumhari maange kangna (mujhse tumhari aankh Kangana maang
rahi hai),
Abhi main banwa dunga mujhe bata toh sahi,
Jaan maang lo main tujhpe jaan waar (jaan nyochavar karna) du, khud nikal jaayegi tu
hass toh sahi, tujhmein nasha pehli tod (daaru) jaisa hai kude (girl), sohniye daru ka toh
naam lagta hai, hum se zyaada tumhari popularity ho gayi hai, tum bahar nikli toh sadko
par jam (traffic jam) lagta hai,
Haa... baat maan meri, mehman meri, tum ho jaan meri,

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

snippet.description:

We used this Adivasi hair oil. We got good result. We recommend you to buy this Adivasi Herbal Hair Oil.🤗

Be alert from them🚨(Place your order with full confirmation by audio call/video call)
Location to Visit : https://maps.app.goo.gl/X54nUhmofLfNY6oP9

This Video has all the things that happen in Summer Vacations . Every Indian in summer vacations going on vacation with family to hill stations like shimla , manali , mussoorie , darjeeling , haridwar , Rishikesh . Indian Aunties going on vacation on their girls trip to south inida exploring Karnataka , loving banglore monsoon weather , south indian food of mysore , dosa , idli , vada , appum  , shopping in local markets for their kids and missing them . Cousins and their night stay at mosi house enjoying mango shake , playing uno cards , discusing horror ghost stories , bhoot ki baaten and creating memories , Swimming class sessions in summers , playing in swimming sessions . Trip with College friends and school friends , exploring the hotel room , collecting toiletries to take back home , clicking photos and alot of gossip . Kaamwali bai asking for vacation , putting up mini swimming pool for the kids in home . Indian moms dealing with holiday homework given by school teachers during summer break , Family trips , horse ridding , trekking , hiking . watching sunsets , sunrise at famous hill tops , creating memories clicking pictures , tourist locations and rush of people and traffic jams , mother excited to go vacation getting her beauty regime by parlour didi , waxing , facial , threading , bleach , dtan , shopping from sarojini nagar to travel , buying gifts for relatives on vacay , travelling by train enjoying , singing eating train food , road trip with family , stopping at dhaba , mom feeding her home cooked food puri aloo jeera sabzi , middle class dad driving on highway , kids singing fighting taking pictures on the way to himachal and so much more ..
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 

Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially guests .. Comment down your Fav Part,

snippet.description:
Parliament Speech: As the 18th Lok Sabha session concludes, we revisit some of the most controversial speeches made by prominent leaders. From Prime Minister Modi's striking remarks to Rahul Gandhi's fiery rebuttals, and Mahua Moitra's bold statements to Anurag Thakur's vehement arguments, each speech left a significant mark on the parliamentary proceedings. The sessions also featured impassioned speeches by Bimol Akoijam on regional issues, Asaduddin Owaisi's critiques of government policies, and Harsimrat Kaur Badal's pointed accusations. This compilation captures the intensity and drama that defined this session.

snippet.title: Mahua Moitra Returns To Lok Sabha With Fiery Speech, Corners Modi Govt On Manipur, Kashmir & Ayodhya
snippet.description:
TMC Lok Sabha MP Mahua Moitra made her comeback speech while replying to the motion of thanks to the President's address. Notably, the TMC MP was suspended from Lok Sabha just months from elections over cash-for-query allegations. Mahua denied any wrongdoing. And in her comeback speech, she came down heavily on BJP and the Modi government. In her more than half-an-hour-long speech, Mahua cornered BJP over Manipur violence, Kashmir, Ayodhya and many more issues.

Episode 4127: Ladki Ka Decision
--------------------------------------------------------
Inspector Pandey thoroughly questions Popatlal on several matters before revealing the bride's decision. Will she finally say yes, and Popatlal's long-awaited dream of getting married come true?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Outspoken is a channel for movie reviews, roasts and recommendations. Intention of the channel is not to offend anyone, but to have an honest criticism. In this channel we review recent films, roast movies in a funny way that has a poor story line , and recommend good films that are must watch but not so known to everyone.

Varshangalkku Shesham is the story of two good friends who are good for nothing. Gulmohar Murali who is a pathetic violinist fall in love with Athramel Annie who is having a secret affair with her brother in law. While murali confronts her, she simply acknowledges and ask him to fly solo.  Koothuparampu venu is a professional bomb maker who had been setting screens on fire for several years and now he is field out due to lack of raw materials for new explosives. Years later Gulmohar Murali and Koothuparampu Venu join hands once again to explode theatres and to set screens on fire. Watch this funny roast to know what happens next and why CM Pinarayi Vijayan had to intervene to stop this duo from bombing the state of Kerala.

മധുരക്കിഴങ്ങ് ശരീരത്തിന് ഏറെ ഗുണകരമാണ് എന്ന് പലർക്കും അറിവില്ല. എന്നാൽ മധുരക്കിഴങ്ങിന് പലരോഗങ്ങളെയും ചെറുക്കാനുള്ള കഴിവുണ്ട്. എന്നാൽ ഇവ പാകം ചെയ്യേണ്ട രീതിയും പ്രധാനമാണ്. എങ്കിലേ ഈ ഗുണങ്ങൾ കിട്ടൂ.. ഷെയർ ചെയ്യുക. പലർക്കും ഇത് പുതിയൊരു അറിവായിരിക്കും 

For More Information Click on: https://drrajeshkumaronline.com/
For Appointments  Please Call 90 6161 5959

---------------------------------------------------
Dr. N S Rajesh Kumar is a Homoeopathic Physician and Nutritionist  in Pettah, Thiruvananthapuram and has an experience of 20 years in this field.  He completed BHMS from Dr.Padiyar Memorial Homeopathic Medical College, Ernakulam in 2003 and Clinical Nutrition from Medical college, Trivandrum. 
0:00 മധുരക്കിഴങ്ങ് 
1:00 ഗുണങ്ങള്‍
3:00 പ്രമേഹ രോഗികള്‍ക്ക് കഴികാമോ?
4:55 പാകം ചെയ്യേണ്ടത് ഇങ്ങനെയാണ്
He is the Chief Homoeopathic Physician Dept. of Homoeopathy, Holistic Medicine and Stress Research Institute, Medical College, Thiruvananthapuram.  Some of the services provided by the doctor are: Diabetes Management, Diet Counseling, Hair Loss Treatment, Life style management , Blood Pressure, Cholesterol,  Weight Loss Diet Counseling and Liver Disease Treatment etc.

snippet.title: 'Manipur Burning, Govt a Mute Spectator For a Year': What Opposition Said on Manipur in Parliament
snippet.description:
Several opposition leaders, in the motion of thanks on the President's Address in Lok Sabha, slammed the government over Manipur Violence. Inner Manipur MP from Congress party, Angomcha Bimol Akoijam said the government had been a "mute spectator" on the Manipur violence for over a year. Leader of Opposition, Rahul Gandhi asked the PM why he hasn't visited Manipur ever since the violence started there in May 2023. TMC MP Mahua Moitra also slammed the government for not stopping the violence in a "burning Manipur".
#manipur #parliament #manipurviolence #loksabha

Hey there, welcome back to Itlu Mee Anjali Pavan youtube channel,  We're thrilled to share a very special vlog with you today. Join us as we dive into the heartwarming birthday celebrations of our dear friend Big Boss Srisatya. The highlight? विगत दिनों ऋषिकेश के विश्व-प्रसिद्ध त्रिवेणी घाट पर सदानीरा मॉं गंगा और राम कथा की पुण्य धारा के संगम का सुयोग बना था। उस रात देव नदी की दिव्य-धाराओं के सानिध्य ने मुझे माध्यम बनाकर रामकथा मंदाकिनी की धारा को जो अपूर्व प्रवाह सौंपा वह स्वयं मेरे लिए भी किसी चमत्कार से कम नहीं था। उस पवित्र-योग के पुण्य-प्रसाद स्वरूप उस ऊर्जा-सत्र का यह अंश आप सभी आस्थावानों को सादर समर्पित है। 🙏🏻❤️
#kumarvishwas #ganga #rishikesh #haridwar 
00:00 भगवान राम के पूर्वज त्रिशंकु
03:50 मम तनु-वितरण-समये हरता देया न मे हरिता (रहीम)
10:35 क्यों कपिल मुनि ने राजा सगर के पुत्रों को भस्म किया था?
15:35 भजमन राम चरण सुखदाई


Follow us on :- 

YouTube :- http://youtube.com/KumarVishwas
Facebook :- https://www.facebook.com/KumarVishwas
Twitter :- https://twitter.com/DrKumarVishwas
Instagram :- https://www.instagram.com/KumarVishwas

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

Apne Apne Ram    : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneRamOfficial
  
The KV Studio        : https://www.youtube.com/@TheKVStudio

Apne Apne Shyam : https://www.youtube.com/@ApneApneShyamOfficial

-------------------------------------------------------------------
About Dr Kumar Vishwas :

The people who make history are the ones who not only give their life to their career but also give their career a new life. When the career is that of a poet, every step is a risk. Kumar Vishwas is one such poet who has gifted himself an era of such a popularity which other poets cant’t even dream of.
Kumar Vishwas is a poet who went beyond the stereotypical norms of ‘Kavi Sammelan’ or poetic functions and made it a performer’s stage. He has mastered and excelled in all aspects in whatever he has done. Dr Kumar Vishwas has been doing this since years just with a mic and his poems and wits in his soulful voice.
His popularity can be guessed by the fact that the audience sings his verses with him, he has crafted a new dimension by rejuvenating the structure and mechanics of Hindi poetry and Kavi Sammelan.
 
Recently, Dr. Kumar Vishwas has started hosting energy sessions popularly Known as Apne Apne Ram and Apne Apne Shyam where he talks about life skills of Shri Ram’s and Shri Krishna's life, and the applicability of the same in one’s own life to over come the challenges and social concerns we come across in our life.

snippet.title: Austria 1 - 2 Turkiye | Highlights | UEFA Euro | 3rd July 2024
snippet.description:
In the UEFA Euro 2024, Austria and Turkiye faced each other in the round of 16. Turkiye found the back of the net in just one minute and started the game strongly. Demiral extended the lead in the 59th minute for Turkiye but Austria was able to score one back later in the match. In the end, Turkiye found a hard-fought victory and moved into the quarter-finals.

snippet.title: Keerai Thokku Recipe in Tamil | Spinach Gravy Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
In this video we will see how to make keerai thokku recipe in tamil. This is a healthy recipe which is very tasty and the main star of the dish is fresh green spinach leaves. We have to make sure that the spinach is cooked just right and not too much that they brown and wither. This side dish can be served along with white rice and can also be served as a side dish for chapathi / dosa or idli.
#keeraithokku #keerairecipe #keeraikootu 

Friends, please do try this spinach gravy at home and share it with your friends and family. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!


Ingredients for Keerai Thokku:
For grinding:
1 tsp Oil
1 tbsp Channa dal
1 tbsp Coriander seeds
1 tsp Cumin seeds
1 tsp Oil
1 Onion
6-7 Garlic cloves
1/5 tsp Chilli powder
1/2 Tomato
1 small piece Tamarind

1 tbsp Oil
1/4 tsp Mustard seeds
4-5 fenugreek
4-5 garlic cloves
2 red chilli
Curry leaves
250g spinch
required Salt
1-2 tbsp Oil extra

snippet.title: 30 Days After The Biggest Election Surprise | Green Shoots Of Democracy Visible? | Akash Banerjee
snippet.description:
A month ago - the citizens of India delivered a stunning surprise verdict - the likes of which had not been seen in 20 years. The hastily put together INDIA Bloc managed to reduce BJP to below a simple majority and shatter any dreams of 400 Paar. 
The election was fought for citizen rights / respecting the constitution / saving democracy - how much of that has happened in the last 30 days? Is democracy in safer hands now? What is the future of Modi and Rahul? - We dig in. 
This episode is dedicated to all the Deshbhakt Family Members who stood by us - though think and thin.

localized.description:
A month ago - the citizens of India delivered a stunning surprise verdict - the likes of which had not been seen in 20 years. The hastily put together INDIA Bloc managed to reduce BJP to below a simple majority and shatter any dreams of 400 Paar.

snippet.title: Indian Family and Foreigner  | Take A Break x @BhaDiPa
snippet.description:
Brace yourself for a comedy spectacle in our latest sketch, "Indian Family and Foreigner"! 😂🏡
In this side-splitting episode, we delve into the chaos that ensues when an Indian family plays host to a special guest – a Canadian colleague of the family's father. What starts as a simple visit quickly spirals into an uproarious whirlwind of cultural misunderstandings, hospitality overload, and neighborhood mayhem.
#LaughOutLoud #YouTubeSketch

It was a nice experience of working with Paula McGlynn from @BhaDiPa if you like this collab please let us know in comments.😇🙌

With Inspector Pandey and his wife by his side, Popatlal meets his potential bride and her family. Will this crucial meeting pave the way for Popatlal's marriage to finally happen?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | નઈ બને તારે મારે | Nai Bane Tare Mare | 2024 New Gujarati Song | નવું ગુજરાતી ગીત
snippet.description:
Groove to the upbeat tunes of Rakesh Barot's new Gujarati song "નઈ બને તારે મારે," available now on @SaregamaGujarati 

Singer: Rakesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Artist: Rakesh Barot,Sudha Tripathi
Music: Rahul Nadiya , Ravi Nagar
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Creative Head : Dhyey Films & Team
DOP-Editing: Chirag kachhadiya 
Production: Satubha. 
Spot: Raju n akshay 
Choreographer: Dipak turi 
Concept n director: Pranav jethva 
Technically Support: Jenish Talaviya
Hair makeup: Hasmukh 
Light: Kalpesh jadav

તુ મને બાળવા  ફરે  જાનુ બીજાની હારે …(૨)
તું આવું રે કરી ખોટા  દેખાવ કેમ કરે …
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે ખોટા ખેલ ચમ તું કરે ,મને ફેર કઈ નઈ પડે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે
તારા જેવી છોડીયો મને સત્તર રે ભડકોની ,
મારા શોમુ ઇનુ ઉતરી ગિયું છે પોની ,
ઓ તુ મને પડવા ફરે એવુ કોઈ કાળે નહીં થાવનું ,
ઉતરી જરે અભિમાન તારે મોપ માં રહેવાનું ..
ભલે તું મને હેરાન કરે મારી પાછળ પાછળ ફરે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
ઓ મને  ને ભાળી તું તો નખરા ઘણા કરે ,
તને એમ લગતું હશે મારા પર મરે છે ,
ઓ તારો ઠાઠ નજારો જોઈ હું પીગળી નહિ જવાનો ,
તારી પાછળ હુ ગોંડો નહિ થાવનો ,
તને હું પડીશ બહુ ભારે ,તુ જતી રે તારા ઘરે ,(૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,(2)
 
 
#નઈબનેતારેમારે
#NaiBaneTareMare
#rakeshbarot 
#saregamagujarati 
#rakeshbarotnewsong

en.title: Rakesh Barot | નઈ બને તારે મારે | Nai Bane Tare Mare | 2024 New Gujarati Song | નવું ગુજરાતી ગીત
en.description:
Groove to the upbeat tunes of Rakesh Barot's new Gujarati song "નઈ બને તારે મારે," available now on @SaregamaGujarati 

Singer: Rakesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Artist: Rakesh Barot,Sudha Tripathi
Music: Rahul Nadiya , Ravi Nagar
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Creative Head : Dhyey Films & Team
DOP-Editing: Chirag kachhadiya 
Production: Satubha. 
Spot: Raju n akshay 
Choreographer: Dipak turi 
Concept n director: Pranav jethva 
Technically Support: Jenish Talaviya
Hair makeup: Hasmukh 
Light: Kalpesh jadav

તુ મને બાળવા  ફરે  જાનુ બીજાની હારે …(૨)
તું આવું રે કરી ખોટા  દેખાવ કેમ કરે …
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે ખોટા ખેલ ચમ તું કરે ,મને ફેર કઈ નઈ પડે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે
તારા જેવી છોડીયો મને સત્તર રે ભડકોની ,
મારા શોમુ ઇનુ ઉતરી ગિયું છે પોની ,
ઓ તુ મને પડવા ફરે એવુ કોઈ કાળે નહીં થાવનું ,
ઉતરી જરે અભિમાન તારે મોપ માં રહેવાનું ..
ભલે તું મને હેરાન કરે મારી પાછળ પાછળ ફરે (૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
ઓ મને  ને ભાળી તું તો નખરા ઘણા કરે ,
તને એમ લગતું હશે મારા પર મરે છે ,
ઓ તારો ઠાઠ નજારો જોઈ હું પીગળી નહિ જવાનો ,
તારી પાછળ હુ ગોંડો નહિ થાવનો ,
તને હું પડીશ બહુ ભારે ,તુ જતી રે તારા ઘરે ,(૨)
અરે જા ઠગાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,
અરે જા જૂઠાડી જા નઈ બને તારે મારે ,(2)
